<HL>
   Law:
   Agency Says NFL
   Sacked Referee
   Because of His Age
   ----
   By Albert R. Karr
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/14/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   LABOR
</CO>
